+Слияние   @{(A 8) (B 3) (@{C D@} 2)
+           (@{E F@} 2) (@{G H@} 2)@}
 
-Merge   @{(A 8) (B 3) (@{C D@} 2) 
-         (@{E F G H@} 4)@}
